1.15,"long_business_summary":"Sunshield Chemicals Limited manufactures and sells specialty chemicals in India and internationally. The company primarily offers ethylene oxide (EO) based products, such as ethoxylates and propoxylates, tris 2-hydroxyethyl isocyanurate, BC 700, hydroquinone bis ether, aminic antioxidants, and urea formaldehyde. Its specialty chemicals are used in industrial applications, paints and coatings, home and personal care, and agrochemicals industries. Sunshield Chemicals Limited was incorporated in 1986 and is headquartered in Mumbai, India. Sunshield Chemicals Limited is a subsidiary of Indus Petrochem Limited."}}